-graniteshares-2x-long-coin-etf-proof-in-pudding\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4717407-graniteshares-2x-long-coin-etf-proof-in-pudding\" target=\"_blank\">GraniteShares 2x Long COIN Daily ETF</a> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CONL\" title=\"GraniteShares 2x Long COIN Daily ETF\">CONL</a></span>) for Seeking Alpha in late August. For the second time this year, I rated CONL a 'sell' and made the argument that the proof was in the pudding on the fund. At</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1383032511/image_1383032511.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742701-graniteshares-2x-long-coin-etf-fortune-favors-the-brave", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 22:19:26"}, {"id": "4742699", "title": "Zumiez Is Recovering, But The Price Already Discounts A Full Turnaround", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/516750419/image_516750419.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Skateboarder falling off of railing in skate park\" data-id=\"516750419\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/516750419/image_516750419.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/516750419/image_516750419.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/516750419/image_516750419.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/516750419/image_516750419.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/516750419/image_516750419.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/516750419/image_516750419.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/516750419/image_516750419.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/516750419/image_516750419.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Thomas Barwick/DigitalVision via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><b>Zumiez Inc.</b> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ZUMZ\" title=\"Zumiez Inc.\">ZUMZ</a></span>) reported a <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4368139-zumiez-gaap-eps-of-0_06-beats-0_03-revenue-of-222_48m-beats-0_44m\">great 3Q24</a>, with comparables up 7.5% (up from Q2 and Q1), and guiding for a similar quarter in 4Q24. The company leveraged its margins despite lower absolute sales (calendar shift).</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/516750419/image_516750419.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742699-zumiez-is-recovering-but-the-price-already-discounts-a-full-turnaround", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 22:13:22"}, {"id": "4742696", "title": "Droning On About Defense: Why AeroVironment Is A Weapon Of Choice", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/956306692/image_956306692.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"A flying drone\" data-id=\"956306692\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"6674px\" height=\"5338px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/956306692/image_956306692.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/956306692/image_956306692.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/956306692/image_956306692.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/956306692/image_956306692.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/956306692/image_956306692.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/956306692/image_956306692.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/956306692/image_956306692.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/956306692/image_956306692.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Yagi Studio</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Introduction</h2> <p><em>\u201cIdiots.\u201d</em></p> <p>That's what Elon Musk called the producers of the F-35, the fighter jet program led by Lockheed Martin (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/LMT\" title=\"Lockheed Martin Corporation\">LMT</a>).</p> <p>According to <a href=\"https://www.businessinsider.com/elon-musk-f35-idiots-building-unmanned-jets-drone-warfare-doge-2024-11?international=true&amp;r=US&amp;IR=T\" rel=\"nofollow\">Business Insider</a>, Elon Musk tweeted <em>\u201cMeanwhile, some idiots are still building manned fighter jets</em></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/956306692/image_956306692.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742696-droning-on-about-defense-why-aerovironment-is-a-weapon-of-choice", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 22:02:51"}, {"id": "4742694", "title": "Zoetis: Are Competition And Price Increases A Cause For Concern?", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155002603/image_2155002603.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Fluffy little dog getting a haircut at pet groomer\" data-id=\"2155002603\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155002603/image_2155002603.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155002603/image_2155002603.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155002603/image_2155002603.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155002603/image_2155002603.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155002603/image_2155002603.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155002603/image_2155002603.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155002603/image_2155002603.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155002603/image_2155002603.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Kathrin Ziegler/DigitalVision via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Introduction</h2> <p>Zoetis reported a great quarter a month ago despite its <strong>shares not enjoying a good market reaction</strong>. Shares were down after earnings, but have recovered since and are pretty much at the same level</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155002603/image_2155002603.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742694-zoetis-competition-price-increases-cause-for-concern", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 21:52:23"}, {"id": "4742693", "title": "Johnson & Johnson Is A Better Dividend Stock Than Amgen In Our View", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2161348037/image_2161348037.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Pfizer, Johnson &amp; Johnson (J&amp;J), GSK, AbbVie, AstraZeneca, Sanofi, Bayer, Novo Nordisk, Amgen. Assorted pharmaceutical companies\" data-id=\"2161348037\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2161348037/image_2161348037.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2161348037/image_2161348037.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2161348037/image_2161348037.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2161348037/image_2161348037.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2161348037/image_2161348037.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2161348037/image_2161348037.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2161348037/image_2161348037.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2161348037/image_2161348037.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Robert Way</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>JNJ and AMGN stock: previous thesis and Q3 recap</h2> <p>My last article on <strong>Johnson &amp; Johnson</strong> (NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/JNJ#hasComeFromMpArticle=true#source=section%3Amain_content%7Cbutton%3Abody_link\" title=\"Johnson &amp; Johnson\">JNJ</a>) was published back in October 2024. That article was <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4726000-johnson-and-johnson-you-need-to-look-at-this-chart-rating-upgrade\">entitled</a> \u201cJohnson &amp; Johnson: You Need To Look At This Chart (Rating</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2161348037/image_2161348037.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742693-johnson-and-johnson-better-dividend-stock-than-amgen-in-our-view", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 21:50:52"}, {"id": "4742700", "title": "KULR Technology: Bearish Technicals, But Could Be An Acquisition Target", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1699116086/image_1699116086.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Astronaut Ventures into Space on a Daring Rocket Ride\" data-id=\"1699116086\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1699116086/image_1699116086.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1699116086/image_1699116086.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1699116086/image_1699116086.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1699116086/image_1699116086.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1699116086/image_1699116086.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1699116086/image_1699116086.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1699116086/image_1699116086.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1699116086/image_1699116086.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">mikkelwilliam</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The lithium price remains near the lows, weighing on lithium mining companies.</p> <p></p> <p>The chart shows the continued weakness in lithium carbonate prices. Lithium is a critical metal for lithium-ion rechargeable batteries. KULR Technology Group, Inc. (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/KULR\" title=\"KULR Technology Group, Inc.\">KULR</a></span>) offers</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1699116086/image_1699116086.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742700-kulr-technology-bearish-technicals-could-be-acquisition-target", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 21:45:27"}, {"id": "4742689", "title": "3 Reasons Deckers Outdoor Stock Is On My Holiday Shopping List", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2157697910/image_2157697910.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Hoka Shoes at Grand Indonesia Mall\" data-id=\"2157697910\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2157697910/image_2157697910.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2157697910/image_2157697910.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2157697910/image_2157697910.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2157697910/image_2157697910.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2157697910/image_2157697910.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2157697910/ima